snippet.title: [DS MODS] Wario Time v2! - New Super Mario Bros. Mod Update
snippet.description:
IF YOU EXPERIENCED ANY IN-GAME ISSUES, PLEASE RE-DOWNLOAD THE FIXED PATCH

DOWNLOAD NOW! - https://nsmbhd.net/file/Ty1cXIVS99q6FkaV/Wario-Time-Patch-Update-v3.xdelta
More info here - https://nsmbhd.net/thread/5771-wario-time-wario-in-nsmbds-mod/

Thanks for watching! Make sure to subscribe for more mods like this!

This is V2 of my New Super Mario Bros. hack - Wario Time! - which puts Wario in the world of New Super Mario Bros! In this update, you must collect gems in order to unlock a super secret! Wario has a new, but familiar ability to assist you in your adventure.
